metadata.name: Joyful
metadata.description:
You can find fun in any situation if you work your head in search for it. This portrait depicts how joyful I am if I'm not afraid of cats in my head, and it made me smile. 

-Anz

.
Submission for TubbyxUwu art contest in April 2022. Characters painted are based on Uwu and TubbyCat characters as per allowed for the contest. 
.
Estimated 36 hours of painting on Adobe Photoshop with Huion HS611.
